⚠️ 10. Corner Cases (IMPORTANT)
❗ 1. Data skew
One key has too many values

👉 Reducer bottleneck

❗ 2. Network overhead

Shuffle phase = heavy network usage

❗ 3. Small tasks overhead

Too many small jobs → inefficient

❗ 4. Fault tolerance

If mapper fails → rerun task


